Name:               RESTng
Version:            0.1
Synopsis:           A framework for writing RESTful applications.
Description:        RESTng is still experimental and incomplete, but many implemented features may be of interest, including: grids for presentation, 
                    hierarchical URLs automatic handling, ORM generates tables from haskell records.
Category:           Web
License:            OtherLicense
